                            <comment id="13901738" author="jdcryans" created="Fri, 14 Feb 2014 18:23:49 +0000"  >&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+      This package is experimental quality software and is only meant to be a base
+      for future developments. The current implementation offers the following
+      features:
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can stop saying that now, it&apos;s even enabled by default since 0.96.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+          &amp;lt;property&amp;gt;
+           &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;hbase.replication&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;
+           &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;true&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;
+          &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Not necessary anymore.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+      Considering 1 rs, with ratio 0.1
+      Getting 1 rs from peer cluster # 0
+      Choosing peer 10.10.1.49:62020
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Those log lines don&apos;t even exist anymore.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+        $HBASE_HOME/bin/hbase org.apache.hadoop.hbase.mapreduce.replication.VerifyReplication --help
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at the current code, it expects -h or --h. Not sure if --help was ever true or when it was changed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So that documentation needs a complete revamp. I&apos;m fine if we want to just document VerifyReplication in the ref guide but the right thing to do would be to rewrite it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13901853" author="gustavoanatoly" created="Fri, 14 Feb 2014 19:45:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jdcryans&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jdcryans&quot;&gt;Jean-Daniel Cryans&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you for review. An alternative we could do is fix the points listed above and publish it, while this, the documentation is being rewritten. Thus the users would have something to guide about verify replication.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=yuzhihong%40gmail.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;yuzhihong@gmail.com&quot;&gt;Ted Yu&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jdcryans&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jdcryans&quot;&gt;Jean-Daniel Cryans&lt;/a&gt; what do you think about this alternative?&lt;/p&gt;

